  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/3d41cc1c92309f98ef0709844ea2cf41.poster.avif?t=1763820296\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/3d41cc1c92309f98ef0709844ea2cf41.webm?t=1763820296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/3d41cc1c92309f98ef0709844ea2cf41.mp4?t=1763820296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How far can you go up? Get on the JanKenUP! elevator and check it out. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✊ Play rock, paper, and scissors while riding an elevator with no maximum floor. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/db5c13d486db6aafb00879f19c90948c.poster.avif?t=1763820296\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/db5c13d486db6aafb00879f19c90948c.webm?t=1763820296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/db5c13d486db6aafb00879f19c90948c.mp4?t=1763820296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🖐 Single player: unlock all characters, beat your records and get all the available achievements.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205560/extras/cf8d7869010e66e7aeb6891a370b5878.poster.avif?t=1763820296\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\